Important Notes
No Side Effects: Return values are metadata only - they don't affect event flow or projection state
Default is Accepted: If you don't explicitly return, Accepted is assumed
Observability: Return values are recorded for metrics, logging, and dashboard visualization
No Error Return: Errors should throw exceptions, not return a status code
Pure Metadata: Return values don't trigger any framework behavior - they're for observability
