Projection Subscriptions
Whizbang provides flexible event subscription patterns using the [WhizbangSubscribe] attribute Projections can subscribe to specific event types, base classes, interfaces, or use generic methods for maximum reusability Basic Subscription Pattern
Place [WhizbangSubscribe] directly on the method parameter representing the event:
