Precedence Rules
When multiple methods can handle an event, Whizbang invokes handlers in this order:
Exact type match (e g , OrderPlaced @event)
Base class match (e g , OrderEvent @event)
Interface match (e g , IEvent @event)
Generic with specific constraint (e g , TEvent where TEvent : OrderEvent)
Generic with general constraint (e g , TEvent where TEvent : IEvent)
